cscie97.asn4.housemate.entitlement

Enum PermissionType

  • java.lang.Object
    • java.lang.Enum<PermissionType>
      • cscie97.asn4.housemate.entitlement.PermissionType
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.io.Serializable, java.lang.Comparable<PermissionType>

    public enum PermissionType
extends java.lang.Enum<PermissionType>
    Enumeration of all Permission types that the IEntitlementServiceAPI uses, as well as the Permission types that are used by the cscie97.asn4.housemate.model.IHousemateModelServiceAPI and cscie97.asn4.housemate.controller.IHouseMateControllerServiceAPI.
    See Also:
    IEntitlementServiceAPI, IHouseMateModelServiceAPI, cscie97.asn4.housemate.controller.IHouseMateControllerServiceAPI
